(42, 7, 24, 40, 3, 1, 5, 'wilderness', 'Connection of John the Baptist', 'Both passages emphasize John the Baptist''s role in the wilderness. Luke highlights the people''s curiosity about John, while Matthew describes his preaching and attire in the wilderness. This connection highlights the significance of John''s ministry and its setting.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
